ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:37:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食m 記 係咪唔會再加大？</blockquote><br />\n又未至於窮到咁"},{"pid":"231c21d7028f42bb23ecb5372267406db58889f6","tid":123524,"uid":9633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:55:09.000Z","msg":"最大原因係咩"},{"pid":"fb13ed451b3a197713bc9d3e052bd6d99f224076","tid":123524,"uid":17889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最好景係點<br />\n宜家又係咩情況</blockquote><br />\nd錢來得快去得快，無話真正好景過<br />\n依家全家出來打工</blockquote><br />\n即係點？<br />\n要自己文字ff? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d420c2cc6cf11d192b7bbe65be526dada24176","tid":123524,"uid":42429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:02:40.000Z","msg":"咁你中落係邊"},{"pid":"2c8f5086548910ef95a7e3f6f83a4cac49bd77ef","tid":123524,"uid":30576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最大原因係咩</blockquote><br />\n一係我老豆唔洗理財，有少少錢就不知量力幫人𧴯債<br />\n二係習近平上台之後，亦係最大原因"},{"pid":"d984d0aaed1bcafd57bd37b418dbb461fdcc3134","tid":123524,"uid":7716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:10:50.000Z","msg":"窮又唔係好窮<br />\n有錢又唔係好有錢<br />\n咁邊到家道中落？"},{"pid":"9611b92fcd0639fed18d041d4d2d5e2ed7b6f545","tid":123524,"uid":30576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最好景係點<br />\n宜家又係咩情況</blockquote><br />\nd錢來得快去得快，無話真正好景過<br />\n依家全家出來打工</blockquote><br />\n即係點？<br />\n要自己文字ff? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好景咪沙士個陣，老豆應該有過千萬現金，但唔肯係香港買樓，依家仲住緊公屋<br />\n阿媽嫁左比佢二十幾年唔洗做野，依家要係地盤做清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00baf971c40a66a6070f138e0b6bccb1f9619bb7","tid":123524,"uid":58983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:11:47.000Z","msg":"憎唔憎你老豆"},{"pid":"e2560101ce27b433cfbda700ec2cec8f24831a4c","tid":123524,"uid":30576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>憎唔憎你老豆</blockquote><br />\n唔憎，因為佢都好無奈，無能為力咩都做唔到<br />\n同時唔鐘意佢不自量力好人得濟"},{"pid":"75331d20cd153558204457db4f2745dc93f6ae4c","tid":123524,"uid":30576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:15:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你中落係邊</blockquote><br />\n由以前公屋富戶變成合格使用者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e994cda9fa7f49f3f54480b9dfeb86cd635b657","tid":123524,"uid":58983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:17:06.000Z","msg":"本身你係人生贏家，有公屋，有錢 現在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641447c0be266f9626ef5e428d54124dc5ae211d","tid":123524,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:18:49.000Z","msg":"之前過千萬身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083242057c25c261d1ffefb951f6dcf120bbd2e5","tid":123524,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e2ce07d054b71c7a18f3a698438175931cb139","tid":123524,"uid":30576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身你係人生贏家，有公屋，有錢 現在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我老豆肯聽下屋企人下講，做人謙虛d，量力而為，做下小投資，相信應該唔會搞成咁"},{"pid":"b0f650991ac0f94100b67532a806ba78325b4671","tid":123524,"uid":30576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:23:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前過千萬身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過去左，依家要我阿媽比返錢佢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a4cff96cf916fbea53df2c2f2477339082717a","tid":123524,"uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:29:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前過千萬身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過去左，依家要我阿媽比返錢佢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沙士個時有咁多錢都唔掃樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f27101712450e8d10d88580c3869b820c352b22","tid":123524,"uid":11666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:30:18.000Z","msg":"返緊咩工"}]}